<p><strong>Timing:</strong> 8:00 AM – 9:00 AM GMT <strong>Duration:</strong> 1 hour <strong>Market Characteristics:</strong> Transitional volatility; bridges Asian and European sessions <strong>Key Currency Pairs:</strong> EUR/JPY, GBP/JPY, EUR/CHF</p>

